 dobro, jako sigurno.

516
00:17:23,140 --> 00:17:24,780
 Ima, bar se sad mogu

517
00:17:24,780 --> 00:17:25,960
 sjetiti četvora ljude

518
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:26,980
 na koje sam vikao.

519
00:17:26,980 --> 00:17:28,560
 Ti su zaslužili,

520
00:17:28,560 --> 00:17:29,160
 ja sam siguran.

521
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:37,880
 Znak da sam uprostio Bogu

522
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:39,340
 je da sad ne mogu

523
00:17:39,340 --> 00:17:40,540
 više prestati pričati

524
00:17:40,540 --> 00:17:41,520
 o njegove ljubavi.

525
00:17:41,520 --> 00:17:43,940
 Ima dana kad mi se ne sviđa

526
00:17:43,940 --> 00:17:44,780
 kako me voli,

527
00:17:44,780 --> 00:17:46,500
 kad kažem da me voli

528
00:17:46,500 --> 00:17:47,240
 kao zubar,

529
00:17:47,240 --> 00:17:49,200
 da čini ono što je,

530
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:50,920
 da mi buši,

531
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:52,200
 stani mirno, stani mirno,

532
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:53,300
 opusti se, opusti se.

533
00:17:53,300 --> 00:17:56,200
 Ali uvijek sam uvjera

534
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:58,200
 da je to sve što Bog radi

535
00:17:58,200 --> 00:17:59,020
 je iz ljubavi,

536
00:17:59,020 --> 00:18:03,180
 čak i kad su situacije bolne,

537
00:18:03,180 --> 00:18:04,640
 kad me plaši,

538
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:07,860
 kad je crnilo predavnom,

539
00:18:07,860 --> 00:18:09,160
 ali znam,

540
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:12,140
 ne mogu sumnjati

541
00:18:12,140 --> 00:18:13,160
 u Božju ljubav,

542
00:18:13,160 --> 00:18:16,260
 jer je to tako iskustvo,

543
00:18:16,260 --> 00:18:17,160
 toliko konkretno,

544
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:20,500
 koje sam imao,

545
00:18:20,660 --> 00:18:25,940
 ne mogu sumnjati u tu ljubav.

546
00:18:25,940 --> 00:18:27,660
 može se dogoditi

547
00:18:27,660 --> 00:18:28,900
 da pobjegnem od nje

548
00:18:28,900 --> 00:18:29,920
 ili nešto,

549
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:30,660
 ali...

550
00:18:30,660 --> 00:18:31,220
 Divno, divno.

551
00:18:31,220 --> 00:18:31,940
 Hvala ti, brate.

552
00:18:31,940 --> 00:18:36,040
 Ti možeš dodati još nešto slobodno.

553
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:38,680
 U medijima je Željko postao poznat

554
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:39,580
 prije par godina,

555
00:18:39,580 --> 00:18:41,480
 ja sam čitao večernjem listu,

556
00:18:41,480 --> 00:18:43,340
 jer bi imao jedan slučaj u Americi,

557
00:18:43,340 --> 00:18:45,100
 jedna žena došla se,

558
00:18:45,100 --> 00:18:46,860
 on nikad nije rekao to iz ispovedi,

559
00:18:46,860 --> 00:18:47,460
 to je ona rekla,

560
00:18:47,460 --> 00:18:47,880
 naravno,

561
00:18:48,220 --> 00:18:49,600
 najveća kazna za svećernika.

562
00:18:49,600 --> 00:18:50,860
 Ako kaže nešto iz ispovedi,

563
00:18:50,860 --> 00:18:52,440
 onda je eskomunicirana,

564
00:18:52,440 --> 00:18:53,240
 mislim, svećernik je.

565
00:18:54,500 --> 00:18:56,240
 Tako da nije on o tome govorio,

566
00:18:56,240 --> 00:18:57,860
 nego ta žena je došla na ispovedi

567
00:18:57,860 --> 00:18:59,180
 i priznala je,

568
00:18:59,180 --> 00:19:01,940
 ispovedila da je lažno optušila čovjeka

569
00:19:01,940 --> 00:19:02,700
 za silovanje,

570
00:19:02,700 --> 00:19:04,500
 koji je završio u zatvoru zbog toga.

571
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:05,620
 I onda Željko, normalno,

572
00:19:05,620 --> 00:19:06,640
 šta će drugo reći,

573
00:19:06,640 --> 00:19:08,680
 nego ne mogu vam dati odrešenje,

574
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:11,480
 dok, ako ste ga javno oklevetali,

575
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,180
 on ispašta,

576
00:19:12,180 --> 00:19:14,380
 morate javno svjedočiti

577
00:19:14,380 --> 00:19:17,380
 da je prouzet odgovornost

578
00:19:17,380 --> 00:19:18,300
 i reći da ste lagali.

579
00:19:18,300 --> 00:19:19,660
 I žena je to napravila.

580
00:19:19,660 --> 00:19:22,120
 I onda je to bilo u medijima

581
00:19:22,120 --> 00:19:23,180
 u Hrvatskoj je bilo medijima,

582
00:19:23,180 --> 00:19:24,300
 ja sam čitao večernjaku,

583
00:19:24,300 --> 00:19:26,080
 zaključak večernjaka je bio

584
00:19:26,080 --> 00:19:28,220
 zašto najbolje svećernike izvozimo

585
00:19:28,220 --> 00:19:29,540
 u inozemstvo?

586
00:19:29,540 --> 00:19:33,540
 I sad si bio obrosi,

587
00:19:33,540 --> 00:19:35,580
 i sada dobio je tri godine

588
00:19:35,580 --> 00:19:36,760
 od svog biskupa da ide malo

589
00:19:36,760 --> 00:19:37,780
 u misije,

590
00:19:37,780 --> 00:19:39,740
 bio je dugo župnik tamo u župa,

591
00:19:39,740 --> 00:19:40,780
 mu se zvala Empire,

592
00:19:40,780 --> 00:19:41,660
 carstvo,

593
00:19:41,660 --> 00:19:43,100
 na jednom prekrasnom jezeru,

594
00:19:43,100 --> 00:19:44,340
 slavo mi je slike.

595
00:19:44,340 --> 00:19:45,100
 I sad je dobio tri,

596
00:19:45,100 --> 00:19:47,640
 pošto je Željko ušao na neukatekumenski put,

597
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:48,600
 tražio je,

598
00:19:48,600 --> 00:19:49,620
 mogu ja to skratiti,

599
00:19:50,140 --> 00:19:51,460
 tražio je od svog župnika,

600
00:19:51,460 --> 00:19:51,880
 dajete mi,

601
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:52,660
 imao sam to iskuslo,

602
00:19:52,660 --> 00:19:53,960
 dajete mi da malo upoznam Boga,

603
00:19:53,960 --> 00:19:54,960
 što znači biti kršćanim,

604
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:56,720
 župnik nije znao što će s njima,

605
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:57,640
 da je rekao,

606
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:58,060
 pa slušaj,

607
00:19:58,060 --> 00:20:00,520
 sad dolaze dva para zaručnika

608
00:20:00,520 --> 00:20:01,820
 na pripreme za brak,

609
00:20:01,820 --> 00:20:02,380
 pa dođi s njima,

610
00:20:02,380 --> 00:20:04,960
 tako da je Željko slušao župnika

611
00:20:04,960 --> 00:20:06,240
 sa zaručnicima,

612
00:20:06,240 --> 00:20:09,100
 pripremajući se s njima za brak,

613
00:20:09,100 --> 00:20:10,080
 ali poslije otkriju,

614
00:20:10,080 --> 00:20:12,540
 neukatekumenski put upravo zato služi,

615
00:20:12,700 --> 00:20:13,980
 to je katekumenat,

616
00:20:13,980 --> 00:20:15,700
 koji danas je izgubio,

617
00:20:15,700 --> 00:20:17,640
 da nas neko uvodi,

618
00:20:17,640 --> 00:20:18,800
 ne samo informativno,

619
00:20:18,800 --> 00:20:19,880
 nego formativno,

620
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:21,120
 da nas formira,

621
00:20:21,120 --> 00:20:22,340
 da nas uči molit,

622
00:20:22,340 --> 00:20:23,440
 da nas uči što je križ,

623
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:25,820
 da nas uči slušat riječ Božju.

624
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:27,900
 Da, to je možda dobra stvar

625
00:20:27,900 --> 00:20:30,020
 da se kaže onak katekumenskom putu.

626
00:20:30,020 --> 00:20:33,220
 Često puta pripremamo ljude za sakramente

627
00:20:33,220 --> 00:20:35,960
 u nastavi, kao u razredu.

628
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:37,340
 Informativno.

629
00:20:37,340 --> 00:20:37,900
 Informativno.

630
00:20:37,900 --> 00:20:39,000
 I djecu na krizni.

631
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:39,400
 Da.

632
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:40,740
 Neka pitanja.

633
00:20:40,740 --> 00:20:43,920
 A to ti je kao da učiš plivanje

634
00:20:43,920 --> 00:20:45,200
 gledajući YouTube,

635
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:52,100
 ili da učiš borilačke vištine

636
00:20:52,100 --> 00:20:54,760
 gledajući filmove Bruce Lee.

637
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:58,040
 ali dok ne živiš u jednoj zajednici,

638
00:20:58,040 --> 00:21:00,460
 jer na kraju krajeva Bog je zajedništvo

639
00:21:00,460 --> 00:21:01,740
 tri osobe.

640
00:21:01,740 --> 00:21:04,580
 Zato nas uči kako živiti u vjeri,

641
00:21:04,580 --> 00:21:06,320
 u zajedništvu sa drugima.

642
00:21:06,320 --> 00:21:09,100
 Nekad je bilo evanđelje o mladiću,

643
00:21:09,100 --> 00:21:09,920
 još samo ovo ću reći,

644
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:10,420
 ako smijem,

645
00:21:10,420 --> 00:21:11,780
 a ti ako nećeš prihvatiti,

646
00:21:11,780 --> 00:21:12,500
 ja ću to u montaju.

647
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:15,680
 Bilo je evanđelje o bogatom mladiću

648
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:17,820
 kojim je Krist rekao da prodav sve ide za njim

649
00:21:17,820 --> 00:21:18,820
 i onda je otišao tužan.

650
00:21:18,820 --> 00:21:20,800
 A bio je na misli samo Željko.

651
00:21:20,800 --> 00:21:21,560
 Imam je paro napamet,

652
00:21:21,560 --> 00:21:22,280
 cijetlio sam se,

653
00:21:22,280 --> 00:21:24,380
 jer kad je Željko doživio obraćenje,

654
00:21:24,380 --> 00:21:25,780
 došao na neukategonomijski put,

655
00:21:25,780 --> 00:21:28,160
 Bog mi je dao voziv za svećenika,

656
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:30,460
 onda je trebao ić u sveć u sjemenište

657
00:21:30,460 --> 00:21:31,340
 i prodao je sve,

658
00:21:31,340 --> 00:21:32,240
 i kujuštu sam,

659
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:33,180
 šta si moj kuću,

660
00:21:33,180 --> 00:21:34,200
 prodao je sve,

661
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:34,840
 dao ča,

662
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:36,320
 ostavio je samo biciklu.

663
00:21:36,320 --> 00:21:38,340
 I šta se dogodilo s biciklom?

664
00:21:38,720 --> 00:21:40,020
 Ukrali su mi biciklu.

665
00:21:40,020 --> 00:21:41,340
 I onda si kupio drugu,

666
00:21:41,340 --> 00:21:42,180
 ukrali su i tu.

667
00:21:42,180 --> 00:21:44,000
 Jer još sam imao dvije,

668
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:45,780
 rekao imat ću još dvije plaće,

669
00:21:45,780 --> 00:21:46,920
 šta će s tim novcima,

670
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:49,160
 pa mogu si još opet kupit biciklu.

671
00:21:49,160 --> 00:21:49,920
 Dobro, eto.

672
00:21:49,920 --> 00:21:51,060
 I eto, ukrali mi je.

673
00:21:51,060 --> 00:21:53,560
 I onda sam zaključio propoved bio neki dan,

674
00:21:53,560 --> 00:21:55,240
 jer taj mladić je otišao žalostan,

675
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:55,840
 jer nije mogao,

676
00:21:55,840 --> 00:21:56,860
 a ja Željka nalazim,

677
00:21:56,860 --> 00:21:58,560
 sad ne znam koliko godina se nismo vidjeli,

678
00:21:58,560 --> 00:21:59,960
 nalazim ga još uvijek,

679
00:21:59,960 --> 00:22:00,820
 nakon svih tih godina,

680
00:22:00,940 --> 00:22:02,140
 veselog i vedrog.

681
00:22:02,140 --> 00:22:06,200
 Eto, tako ostani Željko do kraja.

682
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:08,440
 Pozdrav svima.

683
00:22:08,440 --> 00:22:09,160
 Pozdrav.

